[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":172},["Reactive",2],{"3S1xVbrJr5":3,"4IDB1KqhIZ":28,"ou4k8ha3so":49,"XKCcxOX1To":57,"F1N7evfJOw":121,"Jtp0a6aQr5":147,"_apollo:default":171},{"mainmenu":4},{"items":5,"__typename":27},[6,15,21],{"menulinks_id":7,"__typename":14},{"id":8,"title":9,"url":10,"status":11,"sort":12,"__typename":13},"57993200-6e3f-4902-beb0-f74f31d6b095","簡介","/overview","published",1,"menulinks","mainmenu_menulinks",{"menulinks_id":16,"__typename":14},{"id":17,"title":18,"url":19,"status":11,"sort":20,"__typename":13},"2a7d3933-eb61-405c-b47c-c7d398a2e0db","字碼表","https://github.com/scj2000/scj-tables",2,{"menulinks_id":22,"__typename":14},{"id":23,"title":24,"url":25,"status":11,"sort":26,"__typename":13},"e2afb80c-ef50-4cda-b811-c4741778cbee","GitHub","https://www.github.com/scj2000",3,"mainmenu",{"articles":29,"tags":48},[30],{"id":31,"title":32,"body":33,"tags":34,"__typename":47},"75407dcc-c619-432b-bb5b-21bd10bdbbfd","Mac OS X 自定輸入法 - 快倉六","\u003Cp>繼先前本站文章講述如何\u003Ca href=\"/content/在-mac-os-x-透過-yahoo-奇摩輸入法平台使用快倉六\">透過 Yahoo! 奇摩輸入法使用快倉六\u003C/a>後，筆者發現 Mac OS X 10.5 及 10.6 系統本身可以製作自己的輸入法（類似微軟視窗之通用輸入法）。\u003Cbr>\u003Ca href=\"/content/mac-os-x-自定輸入法-快倉六\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://cms.scj2000.net/assets/e783feed-9557-449b-9cfd-ccdfee5af2aa?width=544&amp;height=232\" alt=\"Mac Scj6 Cin 1\">\u003C/a>\u003C/p>\n\u003C!--break-->\n\u003Cp>安裝方法很簡單，如下：\u003C/p>\n\u003Col>\n\u003Cli>下載 \u003Ca href=\"http://download.scj2000.net/src/scj6.cin\">scj6.cin\u003C/a> 到 ${使用者家目錄}/Library/Input Methods/\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>登出然後重新登入\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>打開 \"國際設定\"\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cms.scj2000.net/assets/0263483a-bb5a-4f08-9e36-639573767217?width=245&amp;height=228\" alt=\"Mac Scj6 Cin Setup 1\">\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>點選 \"快倉六\"\u003Cbr>\u003Ca href=\"/sites/default/files/Mac-scj6-cin-setup-2.png\" rel=\"lightbox\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://cms.scj2000.net/assets/e1786bb6-2f3e-46ac-ace1-6d30efc566d3?width=677&amp;height=588\" alt=\"Mac Scj6 Cin Setup 2\">\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>要使用，在國際設定(國旗)下選取 \"快倉六\" (或按 [Command]+[Option]+[空白鍵] 選用 \"快倉六\") 開始使用\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cms.scj2000.net/assets/592eefd9-f826-4436-9adb-ecc6c02be8b6?width=365&amp;height=268\" alt=\"Mac Scj6 Cin Setup 3\">\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ol>\n\u003Cp>\u003Cbr>在輸入中文字時，鍵入快倉碼及按 [空白鍵] 可選字，\u003Cbr>如要輸入標點符號，按 [z] [space]\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cms.scj2000.net/assets/0d2920fc-ce2e-47f5-9151-5b45dcd02f2f?width=527&amp;height=239\" alt=\"Mac Scj6 Cin 2\">\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>輸入「輸」的廣東拼音 su，按 [z] [s] [u] [space] (快倉六廣東拼音以 z 前置)\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg src=\"https://cms.scj2000.net/assets/fead2ca8-c3bc-41ae-a4a2-12527e40df08?width=530&amp;height=218\" alt=\"Mac Scj6 Cin 3\">\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>&nbsp;\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>雖然大多數用家因為易用會比較喜歡在 OS X 使用奇摩輸入法，使用 OS X 的自定輸入法機制亦不失為另一好選擇。\u003C/p>\n\u003Cp>參考：\u003Cbr>Mac OS X 10.6 Help: \u003Ca href=\"http://docs.info.apple.com/article.html?path=Mac/10.6/yh/8952.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">製作和使用您自己的輸入法\u003C/a>\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003C/p>",[35,42],{"tags_id":36,"__typename":41},{"id":37,"name":38,"slug":39,"__typename":40},"8b789213-c7fc-4701-b49d-15466cc311ba","macOS","/tags/macos","tags","articles_tags",{"tags_id":43,"__typename":41},{"id":44,"name":45,"slug":46,"__typename":40},"2b3fec4c-f1b0-4cf6-8779-64e48532997f","快倉六","/tags/scj6","articles",[],{"downloadlink":50},{"id":51,"menulink":52,"__typename":56},"e86f942a-6c9c-469f-a3d6-8f9ff475df38",{"id":53,"title":54,"url":55,"status":11,"__typename":13},"f3185617-a034-4b6d-9800-94efca37aaaa","下載","/download","downloadlink",{"tags":58},[59,63,69,71,76,80,85,90,96,101,106,111,116],{"id":44,"name":45,"slug":46,"status":11,"articles_func":60,"__typename":40},{"count":61,"__typename":62},8,"count_functions",{"id":64,"name":65,"slug":66,"status":11,"articles_func":67,"__typename":40},"51bd08c8-6b64-4827-8874-beaafc7c7388","Linux","/tags/linux",{"count":68,"__typename":62},5,{"id":37,"name":38,"slug":39,"status":11,"articles_func":70,"__typename":40},{"count":20,"